### Padrão de views e URLs

```python
# _get_tokens: RefreshToken.for_user(user) → {'refresh', 'access', 'user'}
# LoginView (AllowAny): autentica via SharedUserBackend → retorna tokens
# MeView (IsAuthenticated): GET retorna user, PATCH atualiza perfil
# Refresh: TokenRefreshView do SimpleJWT em /api/auth/refresh

# config/urls.py: health + admin + api/
# api/urls.py: DefaultRouter (ViewSets) + rotas manuais de auth
# Multi-tenancy: ViewSets filtram por request.user.profile.organization
```

